name: This is Teshwin Blark
description:
Teshwin Blark appeared to be a devoted employee of Zephania Feroo until he was 
discovered passing technology to agents of the Communard Republic of Kusht. He managed 
a dramatic escape from Purush and has ended up in charge of their state-sponsored space 
programme set up by the Communard government in Kusht. It doesn’t take long for him to 
realise there is no real space programme to lead. He is merely the figurehead for a massive 
propaganda exercise aimed at raising the spirits of the populace. And cracks caused by the 
overwhelming stress of his position are beginning to show.
